Package: brfinance
Title: Simplified access to Brazilian financial and macroeconomic data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "JoÃ£o Paulo", family = "dos Santos Pereira Barbosa", email = "joao.31582129@gmail.com",role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools to easily access and visualize key macroeconomic indicators from Brazil, such as the basic interest rate (SELIC) and the unemployment rate, using official sources like the Central Bank of Brazil (BCB) and IBGE (via SIDRA).
